racters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"What~?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event103-06-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"That was super-duper fun, huh, guys?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"jaan01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"event103-06-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"That was even harder than it looks... But I think we did surprisingly well, right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event103-06-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Sigh... Ahaha, it's kinda strange. It's hard to believe that we were worried about Kokoro being lost just a little while ago.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event103-06-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Sorry. She ended up being a headache, didn't she?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"sad03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event103-06-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"It's fine! It's like... it didn't feel like a burden.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event103-06-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Yeah, we were running around like crazy looking for her, but... it seems more correct to say that we were taken on a little adventure.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event103-06-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Ahhh, yeah, I think I get what you mean.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event103-06-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"We were all shocked at first, but that free time we had where we were wondering what to do was taken care of in an instant.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event103-06-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Right! I always thought this is what it's like, but I'm really happy now that I've been able to experience it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event103-06-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"This must be what it's like for everyone in Hello, Happy World! who choose to spend so much time with Kokoro.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event103-06-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"I'd say it's always more \"dragged into\" than \"taken on\" an adventure, though...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event103-06-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Ahaha! Hey, but that's just the way Kokoro is, right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event103-06-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Just like being on a roller coaster, huh~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event103-06-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Yeah~! That's the perfect description for Kokoro-chan!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event103-06-054","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windo